<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>They have been inseparable since the start of the year.</p>

<p>And Nicole Scherzinger continued in her blissful time with her handsome Brit boyfriend Thom Evans on Monday as they headed to Yosemite National Park in California for a hike, during which she donned a crop top.</p>

